    "These AI technologies are utilized in planning [66], predicting student performance [42], and teaching and learning [68] to support Nigerian education, as presented in Table 1.Data analytics for decision-making: Educational institutions began leveraging AI for automated data analytics to make informed decisions in teaching processes.",
    "AI technologies, including machine learning algorithms [42,71], were used to analyze student performance data and assessment processes, ensuring consistent evaluation.",
    "From 2017 to 2022, there was a notable surge in research publications due to the increased integration of AI technology.",
